Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.86,0:00:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be much of a guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Priest Biwamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.08,0:00:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There was once a cry  \N that should've been heard in this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No sooner was it uttered \Nthan it was silenced.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.34,0:01:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet even so, it reverberated \Nthroughout the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And it still does.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.86,0:00:32.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,道案内ってわけにはいかねぇが
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:35.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,杖の代わりにはなりましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:36.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,琵琶丸どの…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.08,0:00:51.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,かつて、この国に響くはずの産声があった。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:56.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが誰にも届かぬその声は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.34,0:01:00.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その実、国中に響き続けていた。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:02.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.28,0:01:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Betrayed this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And it simmers within
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.75,0:01:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Rupturing my innards
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.96,0:01:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Swelling a reddish black
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.09,0:01:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the sun burnt skin ruptures
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.81,0:01:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a light  \N in the depths of the seething darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.65,0:01:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirming each other's voices  \N in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.82,0:02:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to stroke with wet fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.99,0:02:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to touch you one day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a light  \N in the depths of the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirming each other's voices  \N in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to stroke with wet fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to touch you one day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,#24 Dororo and Hyakkimaru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Repulsive. \NHow dare you stain the castle of Daigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no place for you to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The castle of Daigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It never has been and never will be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born and raised here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I played here, I trained here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Father gave me that desk. Horses, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,As with Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother always...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Always...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My son...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She is my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You were never here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing here is a testimony \Nof your existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You... Why is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You were here. Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-Then why are you lacking? \N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You are lacking. Just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-Me? Never. \N-Why? Why do you lack something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! If I am lacking something, \Nyou took it from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mutsu and Hyogo. Mother, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I did? From you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So give it back. \NAll of you, give it back to this land!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro's got to be up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't reach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.64,0:05:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Bro! \N-Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Priest, you came. \NEverything's gone up in flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A secret passage. Lady Nui is down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo, wait for me up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I will need you to pull this back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stay by my son's side. \NJust as you have always done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be Hyakkimaru's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He truly has your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you slice through me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You could've severed my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're human.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nay, I've always been losing to you. \NAlways.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tahomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tis my chance to fulfill the contract!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Demons don't give up easily, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, I will give these back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, dang it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just stand around. \NPriest, you wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're leaving me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, I can hold you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I never should have let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've just held you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How I love you, how I love you so dearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:09:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What I should've given you \Nwasn't arms or legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Hyakkimaru. You must live.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let a human and not a demon \Nreside in your bloodstained body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You already have \Nthe embers glowing within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a child who is waiting for you. \NOne who will stay by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-Bro! \N-Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta get out of here. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This way. The fire is spreading, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't breathe in the smoke. \NYou'll burn your lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tahomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me for making you feel so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will stay by your side forever now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never leave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, it all ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-Priest! \N-You're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru too? Good. \NI'll pull you up. Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,One second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ready. \N-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro's arms are soft and warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He finally got them back, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty. The sky is pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo. You are pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:13:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What... Shut up, whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you can see? You see my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-Careful, you'll fall. \N-You can see my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the closure to your fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch it closely, \Nwith those eyes of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord, grave news.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I hesitate to tell you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The castle is burning, \Nand it has spread throughout.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master's residence \Nhas been burnt down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:14:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master and Lady Nui \Nhave gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It is feared that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We will crush the Asakura. Onward, march!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,To fend off the Asakura army,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,innumerable men lost their lives  \N for Daigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The final demon statue  \N also crumbled and fell that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet, there was nobody to notice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I get what you're saying about \Nnot relying on samurai to make a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And we all would if we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But we don't have that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know \Nhow to use swords and spears.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I'm not talking about \Nthat kind of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what do you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't use samurai or demons. \NWe won't do wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what else but money?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but where do we get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't suffer like this if we had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit far from here. \NBut it's a hidden mountain of gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get it in a couple of days, \Nso be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's quite a bold idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who told me \Nto think of how to use the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't meant it so profoundly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A land where the people \Nbuild up their own country, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'd never thought of it \Nbecause I'm one of the samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You? A samurai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind. \NBy the way, where's Hyakkimaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems to be deep in thought \Never since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so I told him about my plans \Nto cheer him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he left, saying he had something \Nhe wanted to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Check? Check what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He just said \Nit was something about himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he wants to see \Nif the body he regained works okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"HALL OF HELL"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you've regained everything \Nfrom the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How is this land you're finally seeing? \NIs it beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The land and its people \Nhas bled too much for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nay, they will keep bleeding for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't let it go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In this world, \Nyou either kill or be killed. So be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I will live through this hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If the demons wish for a human, \NI will just feed them another.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You will feed me to them again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And why not? I am a samurai lord. \NI wish for nothing but total rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I will strike as many deals \Nwith the demons as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If I've ever been wrong, \Nit has only been once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have left you to the midwife.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've strangled you \Nwith my own two hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You must despise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I die, my soul shall reign \Ntogether with my son Tahomaru
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as a demon protecting this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No. He wasn't at the castle, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he'd be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe's he's already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He may have left on another journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah right, he never would!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he go without telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy has just been born.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because he's regained his body. \NI mean his heart and mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He must leave the path of evil \Nand retrace the path of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's killed too many people \Nfor it to be easy to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro's mama and brother are dead now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.53,0:19:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him it's not his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If Hyakkimaru walks down \Nthe wrong path again, you may not be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps that's \Nwhat he's gone off to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:19:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The path I take.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Does not lead that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I am human.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you become a demon, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Live on as a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't turned to these demons \Nthat day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.51,0:20:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had succeeded my reign,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the prosperity that I have so desired  \N may have...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Within you is a strength to live on,  \N a strength that demons craved so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.42,0:21:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru has gone,  \N and Dororo walks on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Warring States Era draws near.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet, Biwamaru believes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.22,0:21:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That something more than blood and despair \Nlies ahead for those two young souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:11.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,穢らわしい…我が醍醐の城を穢すな！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:15.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,本来ならばここは…貴様などが入れる場所ではない！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:16.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,醍醐の城…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:18.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なら俺のだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:22.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほざくな…貴様のものであるものか！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:28.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここは…私の城だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:30.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生まれてよりここで育った！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:33.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この庭を走り、剣を学んだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:37.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これは私の部屋だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:41.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,文机は父上からいただいた！馬もだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:42.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,母上もそうだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:45.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,母上は…いつも…！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:50.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いつも…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:54.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,母上は…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:56.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,坊や…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:02.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,母上…？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:04.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私の母上だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:08.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ぐぅっ！貴様はここにいなかった！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:12.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここには貴様の思い出など、何ひとつ刻まれてはいない！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:15.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前…なぜだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:16.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何がだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:19.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前はいた…ここにずっと！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:21.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ！貴様とは違う！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:24.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ならなぜ足りない！\Nなに？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:27.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前は足りない、俺のように
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:31.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,くっ…誰が…\Nなぜだ！なぜ足りない！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:35.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だぁまれぇ！だとすれば貴様が奪ったのだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:38.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,陸奥と兵庫も！母上も…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:41.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺が…お前…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:45.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だから返せ！\N貴様のすべてをこの国に！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:08.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきはきっとあそこだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:10.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,けどもう道が…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.64,0:05:14.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…あにき、あにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:16.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきぃー！\Nどろろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:21.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,坊さん！来てくれたのかい？この先は火の海で…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:22.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何やってんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:25.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,奥方がね、抜け道をさ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:26.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はっ…おばちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:29.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ。そこで待っていてください。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:32.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あとで引き上げてもらわねばなりませぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:33.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらも行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:37.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:43.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの子のそばにいてください。これまでのように
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:47.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おばちゃん…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:15.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸の…母上か
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:19.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,親子とは…似るものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:21.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなたは？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:10.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぜ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:15.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぜ外した！今の一太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:18.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私の首も落とせたはず…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:20.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぜ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:22.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わからない…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:25.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ただ…同じだ。お前も。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:28.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前は…人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:34.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,敵わぬ、な…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:40.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや。私はずっと…敵わなかったのだ。ずっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:44.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,多宝丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:03.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今こそ約定を！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:05.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:10.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神とは…往生際が悪いな…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:17.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兄上…！これは…お返しいたします…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:34.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,んだよ！どうなってんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:37.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,見ちゃいられねぇ。坊さん！あと頼むぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:41.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お待ち…おい、私だけ留守番かい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:25.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…あにう…え…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:34.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:37.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,坊や…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:41.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やっとそなたを…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:46.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あのとき、何があろうとこの手を離すべきではなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:50.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ただそなたを抱いていればよかった…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:55.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どれほどそなたを愛しいと…愛しいと…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:09:59.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あったかい…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:05.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸、許せ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:11.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わしがお前にやるべきものは、手でも足でもなかったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:14.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よいか百鬼丸。生きろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:19.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その血にまみれた身体に、鬼ではなく人を宿せ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:23.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その火種は手に入れたはず
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:33.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきー！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:36.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おゆきなさい。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:40.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなたには待っている子が、そばにいてくれるあの子がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:42.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ゆけ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:07.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっ…か…ちゃん…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:17.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきー！\Nどろろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:19.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここにいたら燃えちまう！早く！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:22.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こっちだ！急がねぇと入り口にも火が回ってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:26.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,煙吸い込むんじゃねぇぞ、肺が焼けちまうからな！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:39.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,母…上…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:41.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,多宝丸。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:47.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,許してください。さびしい思いをさせました。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:53.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でもこれからはずっと…母はあなたのそばにおりますよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:54.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,安心なさい、
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:57.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もう決して離れません
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これで…やっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:21.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,坊さん！\Nおぉ！戻ったかい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:26.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸も一緒かい。よかった！さぁ引っ張るよ、いいかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:27.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ち…ちょっと待ってくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:33.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,上げてくれ\Nよしきた！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:42.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,助かった…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:45.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきの腕柔らかくてあったけーや。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やっと取り返したんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:52.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,綺麗\N空…綺麗だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:53.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,空？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:57.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ…綺麗だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:13:01.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ば…！バカあにき！こんなときに何言って！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:05.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,えっ？目が…おいらの顔見えんのかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:10.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい！落っこちちまうよ！\N嘘じゃねぇよな！おいらの顔見えんのかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:12.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいあにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:19.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これがお前さんの因果の節目だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:23.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,しっかり見ておくんだね、その目で
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:26.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はっ…なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:44.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿！一大事にございます
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:48.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まことに…申し上げにくいことながら…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:49.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,申せ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:53.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,御城内から出火。城郭づたいに延焼し、
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:56.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若君様の御屋敷が焼失いたしました。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:14:00.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若君、ならびに奥方様は行方知れず。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:02.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おそらくは…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:03.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大儀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:09.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,朝倉を叩く！進め！進めぇーい！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:15.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この日、朝倉の軍を食い止めるために
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:18.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,醍醐が落とした命は数知れず
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:26.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そして…地獄堂で最後の鬼神像が崩れ落ちたことを知る者も…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:29.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,また、なかった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:36.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そりゃおめぇの言う、\N武士に頼らないで自分たちの力で生活を立てるってのはわかるし、
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:40.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうしたいのはみんな同じだけどよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:43.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その力ってのが問題だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:46.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいら たちに刀や槍は扱えねぇよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:50.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,違う違う。おいらが言ってんのはそんな力じゃねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:52.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,では、それはどのような？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:55.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいか。よく聞けよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:57.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,カネだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:01.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,士の力も鬼神の力も借りねぇ。戦もしねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:04.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,となると残るのはカネの力しかねぇだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:07.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいおいそんなカネどこにあるってんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:10.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんなもん、あったら苦労しねーよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:11.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,カネならある
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:17.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まぁ、在り処は遠いんだがよ。ちょっとした隠し金山ってとこだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:18.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ホントか！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:20.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どこだい？その場所は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:22.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,落ち着け落ち着け。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:26.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ま、2・3日じゅうに取りに行くから準備しといてくれよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:32.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なるほどねぇ…そいつはまた思い切った考え方だねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:35.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだ、聞いてたのかよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:38.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,坊さんが言ってたんだぜ？カネをどう使うか考えろってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:41.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そこまで考えてたわけじゃない。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:45.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,民が自分たちの国を自らの手で作る、か。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:50.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こに思い至らなかったのは、しょせん侍側だからだろうかねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:53.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,え？侍側？坊さんが？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:57.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いやいや。ところで、百鬼丸はどうしたんだい。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:01.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あのときからずいぶん考え込んでる様子だが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:06.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うん。だから元気付けようと思って今のハナシしたんだけどさ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:09.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そしたら急にちょっと確かめるモンがあるって出かけてった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:12.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,確かめる？何をだい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:16.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それが…自分のことだとか何とかボソボソ言うばっかでさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:20.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おおかた取り戻した身体がちゃんとしてるかどうかってことじゃねぇかな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:03.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すべて…鬼神から取り戻したか。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:09.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その目で初めて見るこの国はどうじゃ。美しいか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:13.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,麗では…ない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:15.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうであろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:19.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前のために国も民もどれほど血を流したか。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:23.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや、これからも流し続けねばなるまい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:26.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが…この国は終わらせぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:31.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この世は喰い喰われるが慣らいじゃ。\N喰うことをやめれば喰われる。なればこそ、
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:35.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わしは止まらぬ。この地獄にとどまり続けよう。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:40.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神が人を欲しいと言うなら、また喰わせるまで！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:43.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,また俺を喰わせるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:49.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,知れたこと！武将と生まれたからには天下取りに勝る望みなどない。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:53.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そのためには鬼神の力に頼ることも厭わぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:59.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,過ちを犯したとすればただひとつ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:03.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの日、お前を産婆などに任せずこの手で…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:07.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この手で息の根を止めるべきであった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:11.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,憎かろう…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:16.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,死せばこの身、魂魄となりて我が子多宝丸と
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:19.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この地を守る鬼神となろう！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:29.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まだ戻ってこないのかい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:32.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うん…城のほうにもいなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:34.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すぐ戻ってくるって言ったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:40.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ひょっとするともうこの辺りにゃいないのかもしれないねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:42.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,えっ？どういうことだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:46.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,また旅に出たのかもしれないってことさ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:48.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんでだよ！そんなわけねぇだろ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:52.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらに一言も言わねぇで、なんで行っちまうんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:54.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まぁまぁ落ち着きな。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:58.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの子はね、やっと生まれたとこなのさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:03.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや、身体を取り戻したからじゃないよ？心持ちのことさ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:04.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだよそれ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:11.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,半分行きかけてた修羅の道を抜けて、\N人の道を歩き直さなきゃいけねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:16.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ただそうするにしちゃあ、ずいぶんと人を殺めてきたからねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:17.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そりゃまぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:21.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきのおっかちゃんも弟も死んじまったしな。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.53,0:19:25.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいら、あにきのせいじゃねぇって言ったんだけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:32.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もしまた百鬼丸が道を間違えりゃ、\Nお前さんだって無事でいられる保証はねぇし
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:36.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だよ。あにきはもう大丈夫だって！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:40.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だからさ。そいつを確かめてんだろうよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:42.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,じゃあ、あにきは…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:57.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぜだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:19:59.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺の行く道は…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:03.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そこじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:07.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺は人だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:11.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたも鬼神になるな。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:13.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人として…生きろ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:22.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:26.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの日わしがここで鬼神にすがらねば…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.51,0:20:30.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前がこの国を継いでいたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:33.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わしが望んだ醍醐の繁栄を…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:35.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:42.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神が欲するほどの…お前のその生きる力の中に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:23.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…おいら待ってるからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:26.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきは絶対戻ってくる。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:28.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.42,0:21:41.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸が旅立ち\Nどろろが歩き続けるこの世は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:44.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦国へと向かっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:47.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが、琵琶丸は思う
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.22,0:21:53.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,彼らの行く手に広がるのは、決して血だまりだけではないと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.74,0:22:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Born into this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.37,0:22:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no salvation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:22:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The distorted shape of the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.33,0:23:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet it beats courageously
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.92,0:23:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no turning back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.88,0:23:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even from the path of evil
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Witnessing the withering seasons
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.34,0:23:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We search for the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.43,0:23:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In our ugliness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.27,0:23:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even recognize the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.90,0:23:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As we peel back the skin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.82,0:23:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We are forever tormented by our stupidity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.45,0:23:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the dawn never comes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.95,0:23:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the painful night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.08,0:23:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You who distrusts nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.37,0:23:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be able to love  \N this accursed world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.25,0:23:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we carry the world  \N on our shoulders
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.67,0:23:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to take it back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.05,0:23:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,THE END
